{"tid":954213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教會塌大閘　壓傷六旬婦","createTime":"2018-12-24T12:27:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-24T15:00:22.000Z","uid":53026,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6488d7c09d5136f1d2e0d414c44b2415efde49d0","tid":954213,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T12:27:09.000Z","msg":"教會塌大閘　壓傷六旬婦<br />\n分享<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181224/large/24la4p23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181224%2Flarge%2F24la4p23.jpg&h=3921cbb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【本報訊】一對夫婦昨晚到九龍城出席教會活動後，妻子在教會門外等候丈夫之際，一扇重逾百磅的大閘突然鬆脫塌下，當場把她壓中。其他教友見狀合力抬起鐵閘把女事主救出，由救護車送院治理（圖）。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【教會冧閘】遭壓傷婦人情況嚴重 教會拒回應事件<br />\n<br />\n搶救後情況嚴重<br />\n<br />\n被教會大閘壓中的64歲姓吳婦人，頭、臉及眼部受傷。現場消息指她送院時有反應，但因傷及頭部故要留醫，搶救後情況嚴重。現場是嘉林邊道39號的基督教九龍城潮人生命堂，昨晚8時許，吳婦與69歲姓許丈夫一同到上址返教會後，當時吳婦正在門外等候丈夫，但教會門口一扇4米乘2.5米的鐵閘突然鬆脫塌下，她走避不及當場被壓中。<br />\n<br />\n事發後許大驚報警，其他教人合力將鐵閘抬起救出吳婦，現場所見鐵閘染有血迹。警方及消防接報到場，救護員替女傷者包紮後，將她送往醫院救治。警方正調查事件，案件列作有人意外受傷處理，而涉事鐵閘則事後立即被裝回，但暫停使用。<br />\n■記者黎家駒"},{"pid":"03a99ab84e3310adde73b82a76be259815f62235","tid":954213,"uid":29130,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T12:27:54.000Z","msg":"神的試煉<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75ffa8cc516fc1d9e6e991f8dd932b9dd3fcd225","tid":954213,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T12:37:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86c1833739177404b05cf709694b03d970a1c08f","tid":954213,"uid":35814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T12:39:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c38a20db87580b397d379f9f99623b0ae489f03b","tid":954213,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T12:50:59.000Z","msg":"【教會冧閘】遭壓傷婦人情況嚴重 教會拒回應事件<br />\n24,811<br />\n\t<br />\n64歲姓吳婦人昨晚到九龍城出席教會活動後，在教會門外等候丈夫之際，一扇至少數百磅的大閘突然鬆脫塌下，當場把她壓中，送院搶救後情況嚴重。現場是嘉林邊道39號的基督教九龍城潮人生命堂，教會今早未見有人辦公，按門鐘無人應門，亦無教友出入，不過教會的大閘並沒有關閉，涉事鐵閘事後已被裝回，門柄位置掛上「請勿關閘」紙牌。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：教會塌大閘　壓傷六旬婦<br />\n<br />\n記者曾致電該教會，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一女職員拒絕回應意外原因及會如何幫助女傷者</span></span>，她只是強調已就塌鐵閘的問題作出適當處理。"},{"pid":"4ba86a9ed504883708f89fd98008f870f0f8fabb","tid":954213,"uid":41818,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T12:58:06.000Z","msg":"呢d係神嘅安排嚟！"},{"pid":"046f893804fdf51a80a2d2894f1242b405b41401","tid":954213,"uid":38143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T13:05:33.000Z","msg":"潮人生命堂呢啲垃圾教會"},{"pid":"10da90d37980dd50a28b9cc3bab9a36b3a563051","tid":954213,"uid":100136,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T13:08:48.000Z","msg":"送乜撚嘢院呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n祈禱叫上帝醫好你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b0cc0f0cca45b199fac8a24c37f2fe8baa12d3b","tid":954213,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"046f893804fdf51a80a2d2894f1242b405b41401","tid":954213,"uid":38143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T13:05:33.000Z","msg":"潮人生命堂呢啲垃圾教會"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T13:11:17.000Z","msg":"乜教會有分.............?"},{"pid":"e96b8ff575c56e5213e53c2e895d98aae74b6dfa","tid":954213,"uid":44454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4ba86a9ed5